OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776435066
OL,3,CExtra police drafted in for Britain
OL,4,CFirst march in Manchester
OL,6,FPolice chiefs will have hundreds of
OL,7,Fofficers on duty in Manchester on
OL,8,FSaturday ahead of a Britain First
OL,9,Fmarch and expected counter protest.
OL,11,FAround 1,000 supporters of the far-
OL,12,Fright, anti-immigration party are
OL,13,Fexpected, along with a similar number
OL,14,Fof far-left counter protesters.
OL,16,FPolice chiefs say they want to
OL,17,Ffacilitate the right to protest but
OL,18,Fstress Manchester is "open for
OL,19,Fbusiness" and aim to keep disruption
OL,20,Fto a minimum for local businesses,
OL,21,Fresidents and the community.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
