PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776435066
OL,3,CExtra police drafted in for Britain
OL,4,CFirst march in Manchester
OL,6,FManchester sees around 120,000
OL,7,Fvisitors to the city centre on a
OL,8,FSaturday at this time of year.
OL,10,FExtra officers are on hand and extra
OL,11,Fpolice powers are in place for the
OL,12,Fcity centre, including the power to
OL,13,Farrest anyone who ignores a dispersal
OL,14,Forder to leave an area and enhanced
OL,15,Fstop and search powers allowing
OL,16,Fofficers to request the removal of
OL,17,Fface coverings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
