FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776435066
OL,3,CExtra police drafted in for Britain
OL,4,CFirst march in Manchester
OL,6,FPolice say organisers of the Britain
OL,7,FFirst march, advertised by them as a
OL,8,FSt George's Day parade, have agreed a
OL,9,Froute with police, starting at 1.15pm
OL,10,Fin Store Street, near Piccadilly
OL,11,Fstation, and ending with a gathering
OL,12,Fand speeches in St Peter's Square.
OL,14,FThe event is expected to end around
OL,15,F3pm.
OL,17,FDisruption on roads and to public
OL,18,Ftransport is expected, particularly
OL,19,Fclose to the city centre and along the
OL,20,Froute of the march.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
