FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776435066
OL,3,CExtra police drafted in for Britain
OL,4,CFirst march in Manchester
OL,6,FRick Jackson, Assistant Chief
OL,7,FConstable of Greater Manchester Police
OL,8,F(GMP) said: "The public should expect
OL,9,Fto see a large police presence in the
OL,10,Fcity centre on Saturday as part of our
OL,11,Fpolicing operation focused on keeping
OL,12,Fpeople safe and minimising the wider
OL,13,Fimpact during the planned protest and
OL,14,Fcounterprotests.
OL,16,F"Disruption should be expected but we
OL,17,Fare working with partners in the city
OL,18,Fcentre to mitigate this.
OL,26,@pD@MOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
