OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776435066
OL,3,CExtra police drafted in for Britain
OL,4,CFirst march in Manchester
OL,6,F"We'll have significant resources in
OL,7,Fplace to facilitate protest and to
OL,8,Fensure our local communities,
OL,9,Fbusinesses and visitors to Manchester
OL,10,Fcan go about their day safely and with
OL,11,Fas minimal impact as possible.
OL,13,F"Our officers will police without fear
OL,14,For favour, ensuring those exercising
OL,15,Ftheir right to protest can do so
OL,16,Fsafely, while intervening when
OL,17,Fbehaviour crosses the line into
OL,18,Fcriminality."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@MO]
